{
  "stem": "2133.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the war broke out, and we never had any contact with them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I knew that-- I knew his name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I knew that-- who he was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, he was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he was taken as a prisoner, as a political prisoner, from Brussels, Belgium, because he was working with an underground movement against Hitler regime.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So as I said, it was--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--very unusual circumstances to meet him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he told me that he's going to try to take care of me and see that maybe they don't take me out, because he was working there as a foreman.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What they call that, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In German they had a phrase for it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the camp.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the camp there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I said, there was too many people coming at a time in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were-- we were living in tents instead of the barracks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SIGHS] It was a terrible experience.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had no food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't get any food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For days.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we did get something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got a piece of bread and a bowl of soup once a day towards the evening.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't get-- barely had any water to drink.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were waiting to be-- we knew that we're not going to stay there long, that we're going to be taken out to work somewhere-- either exterminated or taken up to work.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If you were lucky enough, then they took you to work somewhere.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was in Buchenwald at that time for about a week.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my brother-in-law used to come to visit me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Time to time, he brought me a little extra piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
